Cross-compilation GCC toolkit with ELF ABI.

Assembler: i386-elf-as
Compiler: i386-elf-g++

GRUB on OSX: http://wiki.osdev.org/GRUB_2#Installing_GRUB2_on_Mac_OS_X

Also, compile and install: https://www.gnu.org/software/xorriso/
(You might want to use "glibtoolize" in autogen.sh instead of "libtoolize")